1
00:01:32,110 --> 00:01:34,930
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,030 --> 00:01:39,920
[Episode 23]

3
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,280
Lord Chen.

4
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:43,000
Please.

5
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:44,789
Lord Chen.

6
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:47,640
Good morning, Lord Chen.

7
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,039
Hello.

8
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:50,590
So many new faces around.

9
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:52,400
Indeed. We thought
when the Empress Dowager fell,

10
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,460
we'd be in trouble.

11
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:55,710
But unexpectedly,
we've risen to prominence.

12
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:57,570
Now we're riding high on success.

13
00:01:57,870 --> 00:02:00,130
I haven't been sleeping well these days,

14
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,000
afraid

15
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:02,950
it's all just a fleeting dream.

16
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:03,310
Lord Chen.

17
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:04,560
Don't you get it yet?

18
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:07,240
We thought Prince Duan was formidable,

19
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,590
but now we realize

20
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,280
the more ruthless one

21
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,600
is above him.

22
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,080
Lord Chen is right.

23
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:16,000
Who gets promoted
and who loses their life—

24
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,590
it's all within

25
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:19,360
the Emperor's control.

26
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,460
Do you think

27
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:23,280
His Majesty will seek to

28
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,910
settle scores with us later?

29
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:26,310
What scores would there be?

30
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:28,970
The Emperor
and the Empress Dowager are family.

31
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:31,160
All these years, we've diligently

32
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,910
served His Majesty.

33
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,590
If anyone would have scores to be settled,

34
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:36,520
it should be

35
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,880
the other faction's.

36
00:02:41,780 --> 00:02:42,710
Did you see that?

37
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,600
They avoid us like the plague.

38
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:48,960
A bunch of opportunists.

39
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:52,460
His Highness hasn't summoned us for days.

40
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,760
What should we do?

41
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:56,970
We're completely in the dark.

42
00:02:57,490 --> 00:02:59,220
It's better not to be summoned.

43
00:02:59,430 --> 00:03:01,830
His Majesty is displeased with us now.

44
00:03:02,410 --> 00:03:04,350
This is for our protection.

45
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:06,740
That's not right.

46
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:09,960
I saw Lord Mu
enter the Emperor's residence yesterday.

47
00:03:17,950 --> 00:03:21,110
His Majesty arrives!

48
00:03:24,530 --> 00:03:26,740
Long live Your Majesty!

49
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:33,120
Rise, all of you.

50
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

51
00:03:38,820 --> 00:03:39,750
Where is Lord Mu?

52
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:43,430
Your Majesty,

53
00:03:43,930 --> 00:03:44,970
I am here.

54
00:03:45,570 --> 00:03:47,100
The personnel evaluation records

55
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,930
of the Ministry of Personnel

56
00:03:49,610 --> 00:03:51,750
that I ordered you to submit—
why aren't they completed yet?

57
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:52,550
Your Majesty,

58
00:03:53,450 --> 00:03:54,570
over the past decade,

59
00:03:54,570 --> 00:03:57,120
the changes in the court officials
have been complex.

60
00:03:57,120 --> 00:04:00,070
The recording work
is enormous and tedious.

61
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,720
It cannot be completed overnight.

62
00:04:03,370 --> 00:04:05,030
I humbly request Your Majesty

63
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:06,750
to grant me a few more days.

64
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:09,070
These personnel evaluations

65
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:10,870
should be organized annually.

66
00:04:11,940 --> 00:04:13,000
Isn't tracking changes

67
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,480
a simple matter?

68
00:04:15,130 --> 00:04:16,779
Look at our Ministry of Revenue.

69
00:04:16,779 --> 00:04:18,250
The changes we have to track

70
00:04:18,250 --> 00:04:21,170
are the changes in land and population
across the country.

71
00:04:21,170 --> 00:04:23,570
The workload is hundreds of times greater,

72
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,800
yet we still completed it.

73
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,090
That's right.

74
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:28,140
Indeed.

75
00:04:28,780 --> 00:04:29,570
Exactly.

76
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:30,460
Your Majesty,

77
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:34,780
recently, there have been
frequent personnel changes in court.

78
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:35,980
In my ministry alone,

79
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:38,490
including the Left Vice Minister,

80
00:04:38,490 --> 00:04:40,490
we are short five officials.

81
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:42,820
I have been searching for

82
00:04:42,900 --> 00:04:45,500
suitable candidates
to fill these positions.

83
00:04:46,659 --> 00:04:48,150
But unfortunately...

84
00:04:49,460 --> 00:04:50,260
Your Majesty.

85
00:04:53,700 --> 00:04:55,150
I do not agree

86
00:04:55,850 --> 00:04:56,409
with

87
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,310
Lord Mu.

88
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:01,050
If we're talking about

89
00:05:01,050 --> 00:05:03,170
having difficulty looking for candidates,

90
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:05,020
it's obvious that the Ministry of War

91
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:06,710
has it the most difficult.

92
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:10,840
Although the court
has suffered serious losses recently,

93
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:13,700
many talented
young officials have emerged.

94
00:05:14,970 --> 00:05:15,730
Lord Mu,

95
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:18,130
why not promote them?

96
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:21,670
Lord Mu, you mustn't
let your personal feelings interfere.

97
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,610
Your Majesty, you are wise!

98
00:05:23,610 --> 00:05:25,780
I... I would never dare do such a thing!

99
00:05:27,810 --> 00:05:29,850
My ministers, you all make valid points.

100
00:05:29,850 --> 00:05:30,980
I can understand

101
00:05:31,460 --> 00:05:33,060
Lord Mu's difficulties too.

102
00:05:33,970 --> 00:05:35,830
But this matter must be resolved.

103
00:05:36,930 --> 00:05:37,790
How about this?

104
00:05:39,140 --> 00:05:41,200
Is there anyone willing to volunteer

105
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:43,450
to help Lord Mu with this urgent matter?

106
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:49,360
I,

107
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:50,940
Yang Duojie!

108
00:05:55,780 --> 00:05:57,570
Am willing to help Lord Mu.

109
00:05:58,420 --> 00:06:01,700
Isn't this Lord Yang
from the Imperial Astronomer's office?

110
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:03,050
The Imperial Astronomer's office

111
00:06:03,050 --> 00:06:05,780
has nothing to do
with the Ministry of Personnel.

112
00:06:07,290 --> 00:06:07,850
Your Majesty...

113
00:06:07,850 --> 00:06:09,050
Is this appropriate?

114
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:12,020
Since I joined
the Imperial Astronomer's office,

115
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:13,290
I've calculated calendars,

116
00:06:13,290 --> 00:06:14,730
established seasonal divisions,

117
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:16,100
observed celestial phenomena,

118
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:17,290
and divined fortunes.

119
00:06:17,290 --> 00:06:18,310
All these duties

120
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:20,830
require coordination and cooperation

121
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:22,020
with various ministries

122
00:06:22,020 --> 00:06:24,650
and attention to every detail.

123
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:26,120
Therefore,

124
00:06:27,050 --> 00:06:28,810
I think I am

125
00:06:30,460 --> 00:06:32,450
the best candidate

126
00:06:33,650 --> 00:06:34,840
to extend help

127
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:37,490
to Lord Mu.

128
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:43,370
Lord Yang previously saved us
at Mount Bei,

129
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:46,420
and now takes the initiative to help
the Ministry of Personnel—

130
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:49,010
he is truly a talented young official!

131
00:06:50,020 --> 00:06:53,080
If my Ministry of Revenue
weren't running so smoothly,

132
00:06:53,150 --> 00:06:55,180
I would want to ask Lord Mu

133
00:06:55,530 --> 00:06:56,800
to transfer him to me.

134
00:06:58,690 --> 00:06:59,610
Indeed!

135
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:01,160
I second that.

136
00:07:01,980 --> 00:07:04,180
-I also agree.
-I also agree.

137
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:05,960
If that's the case,

138
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,840
I promote Yang Duojie
to Vice Minister of Personnel

139
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:11,970
to quickly compile the records I need.

140
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,550
As for Lord Mu...

141
00:07:18,010 --> 00:07:18,810
Your Majesty.

142
00:07:19,290 --> 00:07:21,020
You've been overworked lately.

143
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:22,100
You should rest

144
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:23,410
at home for now.

145
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:46,560
Your Highness.

146
00:07:47,250 --> 00:07:48,210
By all accounts,

147
00:07:48,810 --> 00:07:51,580
I'm openly aligned
with the Empress Dowager's faction.

148
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:53,400
Yet he not only
doesn't try to win me over,

149
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:56,780
but puts me on the hot seat repeatedly.

150
00:07:57,730 --> 00:07:59,460
I've been thinking hard,

151
00:07:59,850 --> 00:08:02,450
but I don't think
I've shown any flaw anywhere.

152
00:08:03,290 --> 00:08:05,290
Please understand, Your Highness.

153
00:08:05,570 --> 00:08:07,170
Lord Mu, you misunderstand.

154
00:08:08,470 --> 00:08:10,210
I don't mean to blame you.

155
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:13,490
This is just like
the recent failure at Mount Bei.

156
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:14,540
We know for sure

157
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,450
the strategy was sound,

158
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:20,160
but there were just
some unexpected variables.

159
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:24,410
Variables?

160
00:08:25,940 --> 00:08:26,710
The first one

161
00:08:27,690 --> 00:08:29,850
is the strange firearms they possess.

162
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:32,630
Its destructive power is terrifying.

163
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:33,570
The other one is

164
00:08:35,190 --> 00:08:37,600
that the expert we met
on the pleasure boat

165
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:41,169
is not dead.

166
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,500
Noble Consort Yu deceived us?

167
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,610
Even if she deceived us,

168
00:08:56,730 --> 00:08:58,660
if no one had tipped them off

169
00:09:00,690 --> 00:09:02,710
and handed over our undercover agents,

170
00:09:02,710 --> 00:09:04,040
along with Lord Murong,

171
00:09:04,350 --> 00:09:05,920
as gifts of surrender,

172
00:09:07,090 --> 00:09:08,290
I believe the Emperor

173
00:09:08,890 --> 00:09:11,290
wouldn't have made it down
Mount Bei alive.

174
00:09:12,970 --> 00:09:15,570
The one who knew
the entire assassination plan

175
00:09:16,370 --> 00:09:19,110
and was aware
of all the personnel involved...

176
00:09:21,620 --> 00:09:22,670
It's Consort Xie!

177
00:09:30,590 --> 00:09:32,300
That wretched woman...

178
00:09:35,890 --> 00:09:37,120
Hot pot?

179
00:09:37,610 --> 00:09:39,000
Two soup bases too!

180
00:09:39,460 --> 00:09:40,600
We've been waiting for you.

181
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,400
Come sit down.

182
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:43,840
If I'd known you lived like this,

183
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:45,650
I would've switched factions long ago.

184
00:09:45,650 --> 00:09:47,160
It's not too late now.

185
00:09:47,300 --> 00:09:48,370
After we finish eating,

186
00:09:48,370 --> 00:09:49,770
let's play some mahjong.

187
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:51,950
You know what?

188
00:09:52,210 --> 00:09:53,420
Rumors are spreading among the people

189
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:53,850
saying

190
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,030
I harmed the Empress Dowager.

191
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,290
And that thunderstorm

192
00:09:57,300 --> 00:10:00,100
was divine punishment
for my misconduct as ruler.

193
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:01,840
Eat this.

194
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:05,220
This is clearly a rumor
spread by Prince Duan's faction.

195
00:10:05,220 --> 00:10:07,550
Prince Duan values
having a legitimate cause.

196
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:08,420
Those rumors

197
00:10:08,950 --> 00:10:11,480
are all groundwork
for his future rebellion.

198
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:14,950
Put it in the spicy soup base?

199
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:18,400
But the problem is
we can't prove our innocence either.

200
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:20,730
Who's spreading these rumors?

201
00:10:20,730 --> 00:10:21,730
I'll go kill one of them

202
00:10:21,730 --> 00:10:22,830
as a warning.

203
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:23,960
No!

204
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:25,010
Why not?

205
00:10:25,490 --> 00:10:27,670
Suppression will only backfire.

206
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,220
What should we do then?

207
00:10:29,420 --> 00:10:31,200
Fight evil with evil!

208
00:10:31,580 --> 00:10:32,340
Evil?

209
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:35,870
Which sect is it from?

210
00:10:35,980 --> 00:10:37,480
I've never heard of it.

211
00:10:39,220 --> 00:10:40,820
I'm from the Devil's Castle.

212
00:10:42,940 --> 00:10:44,040
Anyway,

213
00:10:44,530 --> 00:10:46,390
if Prince Duan calls you a tyrant,

214
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:48,050
you call him a hypocrite.

215
00:10:48,300 --> 00:10:49,700
If he says you harmed the Empress Dowager,

216
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:51,060
you say he hired assassins.

217
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:52,370
If he says you were struck by lightning,

218
00:10:52,370 --> 00:10:55,180
you say as the true Son of Heaven,

219
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,490
you can summon 81 thunderbolts
with a wave of your hand

220
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:59,820
to strike down on all the other assassins.

221
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,300
Isn't that too exaggerated?

222
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:04,050
Seems quite dramatic too.

223
00:11:04,460 --> 00:11:06,280
What do you two know?

224
00:11:06,850 --> 00:11:08,050
Let me put it this way.

225
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:11,060
If you excitedly share
with other people this:

226
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,340
"Jeez!

227
00:11:12,610 --> 00:11:14,810
I learned something from a book today."

228
00:11:14,850 --> 00:11:18,330
Would you be sharing about things

229
00:11:18,370 --> 00:11:20,840
like the Pythagorean theorem, functions,

230
00:11:20,950 --> 00:11:23,100
prime numbers,
or that pi equals 3.1415926?

231
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:23,980
Of course not!

232
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:26,110
Because you can't even remember that.

233
00:11:26,130 --> 00:11:26,580
But

234
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:29,290
if you go tell others,

235
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:31,250
"Oh my God.

236
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,420
That tyrant

237
00:11:32,610 --> 00:11:33,980
just waved his arm

238
00:11:34,370 --> 00:11:36,220
and summoned 100,000 thunderbolts,

239
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:37,520
killing all the

240
00:11:37,650 --> 00:11:39,280
darn assassins."

241
00:11:40,530 --> 00:11:42,790
Would you go around telling others that?

242
00:11:45,730 --> 00:11:47,010
That makes some sense.

243
00:11:48,130 --> 00:11:49,630
Throughout history, Emperors,

244
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:51,020
to win people's hearts,

245
00:11:51,610 --> 00:11:54,940
would even make up stories
about hiding books in fish bellies.

246
00:11:54,940 --> 00:11:56,840
The key is that
people actually believed them.

247
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,010
Not bad, Xie.

248
00:11:58,340 --> 00:11:59,400
You've got skills.

249
00:12:00,110 --> 00:12:01,710
Prince Duan has lasted this long

250
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:03,310
all because of your support.

251
00:12:05,890 --> 00:12:06,580
Him?

252
00:12:07,850 --> 00:12:08,700
That bastard.

253
00:12:09,610 --> 00:12:10,760
He's no fun to play with.

254
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:11,760
I'm done with him.

255
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:13,980
But

256
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:15,520
I must warn you.

257
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:18,650
Public opinion battles
are just the first wave.

258
00:12:18,650 --> 00:12:20,250
The real attacks come after.

259
00:12:20,420 --> 00:12:21,680
You better be careful.

260
00:12:22,370 --> 00:12:23,760
He wants legitimate reasons.

261
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:25,890
He won't make a move inside the palace.

262
00:12:27,010 --> 00:12:27,810
That's right.

263
00:12:27,890 --> 00:12:29,150
Xu Yao's book also says

264
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:32,300
he'll only make his move
when you leave the palace.

265
00:12:36,010 --> 00:12:37,610
I've been meaning to ask you.

266
00:12:38,770 --> 00:12:39,970
You mentioned before

267
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:41,700
that the plan in Xu Yao's book

268
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:43,860
was different from my original plan.

269
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:45,630
How did you know that?

270
00:12:46,390 --> 00:12:47,920
I only told Xiahou Bo.

271
00:12:55,730 --> 00:12:57,220
After Xu Yao switched sides,

272
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,420
he told me everything.

273
00:12:58,420 --> 00:12:59,820
He discussed all the suggestions you made

274
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:01,220
with Prince Duan before.

275
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:04,540
That makes sense now.

276
00:13:09,730 --> 00:13:10,580
I got it!

277
00:13:11,250 --> 00:13:11,580
What?

278
00:13:11,770 --> 00:13:12,770
What's wrong, Mr. Bei?

279
00:13:12,770 --> 00:13:13,700
What did you get?

280
00:13:13,770 --> 00:13:14,370
Evil!

281
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:28,690
Braised egg.

282
00:13:31,690 --> 00:13:33,020
I didn't get that right.

283
00:13:33,570 --> 00:13:34,430
Let me go again.

284
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:38,050
Living in ancient times,

285
00:13:38,820 --> 00:13:40,820
not having a bathroom heater is fine.

286
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:42,060
But not having a hair dryer,

287
00:13:42,060 --> 00:13:43,460
that's the real trouble.

288
00:13:46,220 --> 00:13:47,950
Who told you to bathe every day?

289
00:13:49,850 --> 00:13:51,360
After hot pot, I smell all over.

290
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,220
How can I sleep?

291
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:56,740
That's true.

292
00:13:58,940 --> 00:13:59,940
You smell so nice.

293
00:14:00,730 --> 00:14:01,790
What are you doing?

294
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,490
Let me go.

295
00:14:03,890 --> 00:14:04,250
No.

296
00:14:04,970 --> 00:14:06,300
If you keep fooling around,

297
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:07,900
I'll make you take medicine.

298
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:08,870
Why take medicine?

299
00:14:08,870 --> 00:14:09,700
I'm not sick.

300
00:14:10,540 --> 00:14:11,380
Quick!

301
00:14:12,250 --> 00:14:12,730
Let go—

302
00:14:14,370 --> 00:14:14,930
Quick!

303
00:14:19,850 --> 00:14:20,340
Mr. Bei.

304
00:14:20,730 --> 00:14:21,330
What is it?

305
00:14:21,940 --> 00:14:22,340
Dan.

306
00:14:22,530 --> 00:14:24,280
Li Yunxi delivered a letter.

307
00:14:40,490 --> 00:14:41,420
What does it say?

308
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:45,800
Cen Jintian's condition has worsened.

309
00:14:46,950 --> 00:14:49,210
He might not make it through this winter.

310
00:14:52,580 --> 00:14:53,480
[For the Emperor's personal attention:
Cen Jintian's health is deteriorating.]

311
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,540
[I'm afraid he can't make it
through winter. He has compiled]

312
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:55,430
[the planting of Yan millet in a manual.]

313
00:14:55,020 --> 00:14:56,100
How could this be?

314
00:14:55,450 --> 00:14:56,390
[He hopes Your Majesty can go
see him one last time.]

315
00:14:56,770 --> 00:14:58,030
In the original story,

316
00:14:58,190 --> 00:15:00,390
he at least survived until the drought.

317
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:03,300
How did it push forward by so much?

318
00:15:03,460 --> 00:15:04,320
That's because

319
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:07,120
he was hanging on

320
00:15:07,870 --> 00:15:09,330
hoping to see the harvest.

321
00:15:10,970 --> 00:15:13,700
Now he knows the people
will survive the drought,

322
00:15:14,130 --> 00:15:16,260
he has nothing to worry about anymore.

323
00:15:18,180 --> 00:15:19,350
For him,

324
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,130
it's a satisfying ending.

325
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:23,700
How can this be considered
a happy ending?

326
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:25,460
We clearly promised him before

327
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:27,240
that he would live to see

328
00:15:27,340 --> 00:15:29,740
peace and prosperity throughout the land.

329
00:15:30,180 --> 00:15:30,940
But you know,

330
00:15:31,810 --> 00:15:34,270
when we used those words
to gain his loyalty,

331
00:15:34,530 --> 00:15:36,530
there probably wasn't enough time.

332
00:15:37,780 --> 00:15:38,640
That vision...

333
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:42,040
can only remain a vision.

334
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:48,790
He says

335
00:15:49,250 --> 00:15:51,050
he wants to see you one more time.

336
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:53,900
I can't leave the palace now.

337
00:15:54,220 --> 00:15:54,700
I know.

338
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:56,690
-So I can—
-You can't.

339
00:15:56,890 --> 00:15:57,620
Why not?

340
00:16:00,300 --> 00:16:02,160
It's too dangerous out there now.

341
00:16:02,370 --> 00:16:04,370
Prince Duan's spies are everywhere.

342
00:16:04,370 --> 00:16:05,700
I'll be careful.

343
00:16:05,730 --> 00:16:07,860
And I have secret guards to protect me.

344
00:16:08,090 --> 00:16:09,330
We lost so many men

345
00:16:09,390 --> 00:16:10,600
at Mount Bei.

346
00:16:11,170 --> 00:16:12,630
These are all we have left.

347
00:16:12,950 --> 00:16:14,080
And some must be sent

348
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:15,430
to protect Xie Yong'er.

349
00:16:17,820 --> 00:16:19,100
What about Wang Zhao's funeral?

350
00:16:19,100 --> 00:16:20,960
Are we not attending that either?

351
00:16:22,140 --> 00:16:23,940
Let those scholars represent us

352
00:16:24,950 --> 00:16:26,580
and build a cenotaph for him.

353
00:16:27,150 --> 00:16:27,810
But...

354
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:28,580
Wanyin.

355
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:30,620
Don't forget.

356
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:32,550
They are 2D characters.

357
00:16:33,980 --> 00:16:35,210
If you forget this,

358
00:16:36,060 --> 00:16:37,390
you'll be dragged down.

359
00:16:40,190 --> 00:16:42,350
But when you heard about Wang Zhao's death
at Mount Bei,

360
00:16:42,350 --> 00:16:43,880
you didn't react like this.

361
00:16:48,530 --> 00:16:50,130
That's why I remind myself

362
00:16:51,690 --> 00:16:53,560
never to get too emotional.

363
00:17:14,630 --> 00:17:15,359
Wanyin.

364
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:19,160
You must listen to me on this.

365
00:17:21,390 --> 00:17:23,069
If anything happens to you,

366
00:17:25,589 --> 00:17:27,150
I can't go on living.

367
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:37,140
By the way,

368
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,270
your father sent a message

369
00:17:41,490 --> 00:17:42,950
saying he wants to see you.

370
00:17:44,660 --> 00:17:45,440
I guess

371
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:47,760
he's not doing well with Prince Duan

372
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,580
and sees an opportunity here.

373
00:17:49,810 --> 00:17:51,470
He wants to use your influence

374
00:17:51,520 --> 00:17:53,180
to find a new path for himself.

375
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:58,100
Do you want to see him?

376
00:17:58,180 --> 00:17:58,760
No.

377
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:02,780
As long as I don't see him,

378
00:18:03,380 --> 00:18:05,710
he'll forever remain just a 2D character.

379
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:18,570
Your Majesty.

380
00:18:18,730 --> 00:18:20,700
The Ministry of Revenue's Lord Chen,
the Ministry of Personnel's Lord Liang,

381
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:22,220
and the two ministers
from the Ministry of Justice

382
00:18:22,220 --> 00:18:23,620
have all requested leave

383
00:18:23,620 --> 00:18:24,180
saying

384
00:18:25,010 --> 00:18:27,210
they cannot come for an audience today.

385
00:18:37,010 --> 00:18:37,590
Die?

386
00:18:40,330 --> 00:18:40,860
Capture?

387
00:18:49,330 --> 00:18:49,880
Kill?

388
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:53,660
Is Her Majesty asking for water?

389
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:54,860
Water?

390
00:18:55,730 --> 00:18:56,540
Water, water!

391
00:18:56,770 --> 00:18:57,660
Quickly, get some water!

392
00:18:57,660 --> 00:18:58,010
Yes.

393
00:19:18,980 --> 00:19:19,530
Ma'am,

394
00:19:19,770 --> 00:19:22,100
the path is rough here. Please be careful.

395
00:19:22,350 --> 00:19:22,950
It's fine.

396
00:19:26,020 --> 00:19:26,750
Everyone,

397
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:29,480
are you all my son's colleagues?

398
00:19:31,050 --> 00:19:33,290
We were Wang's closest friends,

399
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:35,200
here to see him off.

400
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:36,900
Thank you

401
00:19:37,010 --> 00:19:37,850
very much.

402
00:19:39,220 --> 00:19:40,220
My son mentioned

403
00:19:41,090 --> 00:19:42,940
he worked for an official

404
00:19:43,380 --> 00:19:44,940
who treated him very well.

405
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:47,920
But I didn't know who that is.

406
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:48,840
I wanted

407
00:19:49,460 --> 00:19:49,900
to come

408
00:19:51,460 --> 00:19:52,730
and thank him in person

409
00:19:53,180 --> 00:19:54,580
for taking care of my son.

410
00:19:59,250 --> 00:19:59,930
Li!

411
00:20:00,090 --> 00:20:01,140
Please wait a moment.

412
00:20:01,140 --> 00:20:01,940
Wait for what?

413
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,940
The auspicious time you divined
is almost passing.

414
00:20:03,940 --> 00:20:04,400
Well...

415
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,460
They probably won't come.

416
00:20:14,010 --> 00:20:15,870
There are too many eyes watching.

417
00:20:16,900 --> 00:20:18,330
They must be in a difficult position too.

418
00:20:18,330 --> 00:20:18,810
Right now,

419
00:20:18,810 --> 00:20:21,570
if Prince Duan's spies discover them,
it be big trouble.

420
00:20:21,570 --> 00:20:22,940
Her Highness usually has so many ideas.

421
00:20:22,940 --> 00:20:23,700
What now?

422
00:20:23,810 --> 00:20:24,920
She has no more ideas?

423
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,380
Li, please don't be upset.

424
00:20:26,620 --> 00:20:27,980
The court is in turmoil now,

425
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:29,900
and the confrontation with Prince Duan
hangs in the balance.

426
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:33,010
His Majesty and Her Highness are not
the type to discard loyal servants.

427
00:20:33,010 --> 00:20:33,770
Right now,

428
00:20:33,900 --> 00:20:36,530
they must be heartbroken
that they cannot attend.

429
00:20:36,530 --> 00:20:38,140
If our Wang knows from the afterlife,

430
00:20:38,140 --> 00:20:39,740
he would surely understand.

431
00:20:42,210 --> 00:20:43,220
Of course I know

432
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:45,620
that His Majesty and Her Highness

433
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:47,080
are not heartless people.

434
00:20:47,570 --> 00:20:48,730
But when Wang died,

435
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:50,420
he was all alone,

436
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:52,650
thousands of miles away.

437
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:54,250
Today at his burial,

438
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:55,780
we don't even have his body,

439
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:58,700
and we dare not carve his name
on the tombstone too.

440
00:20:59,350 --> 00:21:00,570
Yet those he trusted completely

441
00:21:00,570 --> 00:21:01,700
and gave his life for

442
00:21:02,620 --> 00:21:04,480
cannot even see him one last time.

443
00:21:05,460 --> 00:21:06,990
I feel it's so unfair to him.

444
00:21:07,460 --> 00:21:08,790
I feel such pity for him.

445
00:21:14,250 --> 00:21:16,410
We are here to see him off
on his final journey,

446
00:21:16,410 --> 00:21:17,410
so he is not alone.

447
00:21:22,940 --> 00:21:24,140
Where's Lord Cen?

448
00:21:27,090 --> 00:21:27,620
Your Highness!

449
00:21:27,620 --> 00:21:28,480
Your Highness!

450
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:31,890
I'm sorry.

451
00:21:32,380 --> 00:21:33,090
I'm late.

452
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:34,610
Not at all!

453
00:21:34,750 --> 00:21:36,460
The auspicious time hasn't passed yet.

454
00:21:36,460 --> 00:21:37,320
Your Highness,

455
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:38,850
this is Wang Zhao's mother.

456
00:21:39,980 --> 00:21:42,110
Ma'am, please accept my condolences.

457
00:21:47,770 --> 00:21:51,290
This is the State Ceremonial Bureau Chief
court robe bestowed by His Majesty.

458
00:21:51,290 --> 00:21:53,980
It was meant for Lord Wang to wear
upon his return.

459
00:21:53,980 --> 00:21:55,290
Thank you, His Majesty.

460
00:21:55,290 --> 00:21:56,490
Please don't, Ma'am.

461
00:21:57,340 --> 00:22:00,340
What Lord Wang did
will be remembered for generations.

462
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:01,540
It is our failure

463
00:22:02,360 --> 00:22:03,880
that we cannot publicly praise
his achievements

464
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,610
and record his name in history.

465
00:22:15,990 --> 00:22:18,050
This unmarked grave in the outskirts

466
00:22:18,710 --> 00:22:20,310
is truly an injustice to him.

467
00:22:21,770 --> 00:22:23,090
My husband

468
00:22:23,700 --> 00:22:24,980
died in the war.

469
00:22:26,180 --> 00:22:28,360
Since Zhao was little, he always said

470
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:30,500
when he grew up,

471
00:22:30,770 --> 00:22:32,770
he wanted to be a good civil official

472
00:22:33,490 --> 00:22:35,290
and come up with many solutions,

473
00:22:35,650 --> 00:22:38,310
and that we can't let people
fight wars anymore.

474
00:22:38,450 --> 00:22:39,080
We must

475
00:22:39,610 --> 00:22:41,940
bring peace and prosperity to the nation.

476
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:44,440
My son...

477
00:22:45,430 --> 00:22:47,690
You've really done it!

478
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:54,050
[State Ceremonial Bureau
Wang Zhao]

479
00:22:55,380 --> 00:22:57,580
With mountains and rivers as your hall,

480
00:22:59,050 --> 00:23:00,510
sun and moon as your torch,

481
00:23:01,700 --> 00:23:03,630
and plants and trees as your beams.

482
00:23:05,090 --> 00:23:05,650
Wang...

483
00:23:07,600 --> 00:23:11,990
[Tomb of the nameless]

484
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:09,110
You're home.

485
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:18,620
Fate willing, we'll meet in the next life.

486
00:23:18,620 --> 00:23:19,720
I hope then

487
00:23:20,250 --> 00:23:21,710
the world will be at peace,

488
00:23:22,330 --> 00:23:23,120
and we

489
00:23:24,010 --> 00:23:25,870
will serve a wise ruler together.

490
00:23:37,570 --> 00:23:38,730
Soul, return home.

491
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:41,450
Do not journey east.

492
00:23:42,380 --> 00:23:44,360
The sea storms have not subsided,

493
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:46,270
a lone boat

494
00:23:47,380 --> 00:23:48,980
cannot cross the vast ocean.

495
00:23:48,980 --> 00:23:50,330
Soul, return home.

496
00:23:51,290 --> 00:23:52,610
Do not wander west.

497
00:23:54,320 --> 00:23:56,250
Desert sands obscure the sun,

498
00:23:58,000 --> 00:24:00,820
dried bones everywhere bring sorrow.

499
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:04,610
Soul, return home.

500
00:24:05,990 --> 00:24:07,220
Do not go south.

501
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:12,240
Miasma fills the mountains and forests,

502
00:24:12,710 --> 00:24:15,040
and venomous snakes coil on narrow paths.

503
00:24:16,090 --> 00:24:17,680
Soul, return home.

504
00:24:18,570 --> 00:24:20,500
Do not go to the northern frontier.

505
00:24:21,490 --> 00:24:22,360
Ice and snow

506
00:24:23,090 --> 00:24:24,520
freeze the world,

507
00:24:25,730 --> 00:24:27,060
and the western jackdaw

508
00:24:27,570 --> 00:24:28,860
cries in deep sorrow.

509
00:24:29,590 --> 00:24:31,590
The river waters are deep and clear,

510
00:24:32,180 --> 00:24:34,510
and above the banks, the maple trees grow.

511
00:24:35,570 --> 00:24:37,430
Gaze out across a thousand miles,

512
00:24:38,660 --> 00:24:40,590
as I grieve by the coming of spring.

513
00:24:41,530 --> 00:24:42,750
Soul, return home.

514
00:24:44,090 --> 00:24:45,420
Soul, return home.

515
00:24:47,730 --> 00:24:48,930
Lament for the south.

516
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:52,180
That was our only encounter.

517
00:24:53,530 --> 00:24:55,390
What kind of person was Wang Zhao?

518
00:24:55,740 --> 00:24:57,540
What were his life's ambitions?

519
00:24:57,660 --> 00:24:59,260
Did he have someone he loved?

520
00:25:00,010 --> 00:25:01,700
Before dying,
when he gazed towards Great Xia,

521
00:25:01,170 --> 00:25:04,720
[Tomb of the nameless]

522
00:25:01,700 --> 00:25:02,900
what was he thinking?

523
00:25:03,770 --> 00:25:04,900
I know nothing.

524
00:25:06,460 --> 00:25:09,660
And now all that remains
is a journey to the end of the world

525
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:11,050
and an unmarked grave.

526
00:25:30,460 --> 00:25:31,550
Cen, I brought—

527
00:25:34,330 --> 00:25:35,680
Why won't you listen to me?

528
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:36,740
It's so cold today.

529
00:25:40,270 --> 00:25:41,290
I'm fine.

530
00:25:42,530 --> 00:25:43,730
Her Highness is here.

531
00:25:46,290 --> 00:25:48,150
Please, no need for formalities.

532
00:25:50,010 --> 00:25:51,470
Thank you, Your Highness.

533
00:25:56,330 --> 00:25:57,290
Your Highness,

534
00:25:58,320 --> 00:26:00,650
you were able to bid
Wang a final farewell,

535
00:26:02,290 --> 00:26:04,290
but I couldn't.

536
00:26:05,700 --> 00:26:07,100
I feel deeply ashamed.

537
00:26:07,590 --> 00:26:08,320
Wang Zhao was

538
00:26:09,420 --> 00:26:11,140
free-spirited and unrestrained.

539
00:26:11,140 --> 00:26:14,270
I imagine he wasn't one
to care about empty formalities.

540
00:26:18,220 --> 00:26:19,080
Your Highness,

541
00:26:19,730 --> 00:26:22,860
I've documented the methods
for cultivating Yan millet

542
00:26:22,900 --> 00:26:25,030
in various field types in this manual.

543
00:26:26,700 --> 00:26:27,300
Thank you.

544
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:32,860
With proper methods,

545
00:26:33,660 --> 00:26:34,730
it can be cultivated

546
00:26:34,730 --> 00:26:35,590
in forest land,

547
00:26:35,650 --> 00:26:36,150
[Great Xia Agriculture 9]

548
00:26:36,250 --> 00:26:37,250
dry land,

549
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:39,000
[Sweet potatoes
have high requirements for water]

550
00:26:38,180 --> 00:26:38,860
as well as

551
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:41,000
[Sweet potatoes prefer warm climates]

552
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:40,900
paddy fields.

553
00:26:41,620 --> 00:26:42,950
Tu'er has promised that

554
00:26:43,050 --> 00:26:44,140
once he enters Yan State,

555
00:26:44,140 --> 00:26:46,340
he will first transport the seeds here.

556
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:49,140
The Salt-for-Services Policy is also
being implemented as per usual.

557
00:26:49,140 --> 00:26:50,350
By next spring,

558
00:26:50,700 --> 00:26:52,210
farmers across the country

559
00:26:52,210 --> 00:26:54,010
will be able to plant Yan millet.

560
00:26:54,990 --> 00:26:56,700
That would be perfect.

561
00:27:02,730 --> 00:27:04,180
Besides planting,

562
00:27:04,750 --> 00:27:07,680
transportation and storage
are equally important.

563
00:27:07,860 --> 00:27:10,250
Yan millet is different from other grains.

564
00:27:10,250 --> 00:27:12,380
It needs to be dehulled before storage.

565
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:13,870
With the right method,

566
00:27:14,770 --> 00:27:15,530
it can be

567
00:27:16,140 --> 00:27:17,430
preserved longer.

568
00:27:17,860 --> 00:27:18,360
Got it.

569
00:27:19,770 --> 00:27:22,010
I'll have
the Ministry of Revenue follow the manual

570
00:27:22,010 --> 00:27:24,340
to inspect granaries across the country.

571
00:27:24,770 --> 00:27:26,180
That will give us a clearer picture

572
00:27:26,180 --> 00:27:28,640
for future disaster relief allocation too.

573
00:27:29,660 --> 00:27:30,490
With that,

574
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:32,980
there's only one thing left.

575
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:36,090
After the drought,

576
00:27:36,810 --> 00:27:37,860
we still need

577
00:27:37,980 --> 00:27:40,460
to adjust crop varieties
in different regions.

578
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:42,790
This way we can prevent future disasters.

579
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:47,990
[Yan Millet Storage]

580
00:27:46,010 --> 00:27:46,810
However,

581
00:27:48,330 --> 00:27:49,810
this is just

582
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:51,110
hastily written.

583
00:27:52,180 --> 00:27:54,210
It still needs to be adjusted

584
00:27:54,660 --> 00:27:56,660
during practical implementation.

585
00:28:03,280 --> 00:28:07,290
[Agricultural Distribution Map]

586
00:28:09,770 --> 00:28:11,660
In just a few months,

587
00:28:12,700 --> 00:28:16,140
you've accomplished what would
normally take two to three years.

588
00:28:16,140 --> 00:28:17,360
I feel truly ashamed

589
00:28:17,730 --> 00:28:19,330
for not visiting you sooner.

590
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:29,010
I am...

591
00:28:29,900 --> 00:28:31,300
I am just a humble subject

592
00:28:31,490 --> 00:28:32,810
of this little use.

593
00:28:36,460 --> 00:28:37,320
Your Highness,

594
00:28:38,250 --> 00:28:39,650
how is His Majesty doing?

595
00:28:40,900 --> 00:28:42,300
Yang feared I would worry

596
00:28:43,090 --> 00:28:45,420
and didn't tell me about Mount Bei before.

597
00:28:46,010 --> 00:28:48,480
Otherwise, I wouldn't have asked Li
to deliver a message

598
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:50,250
and trouble His Majesty at such a time.

599
00:28:50,250 --> 00:28:51,910
Please don't blame yourself.

600
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:55,230
This is Physician Xiao from the palace.

601
00:28:55,230 --> 00:28:57,160
His medical skills are unmatched.

602
00:28:57,730 --> 00:28:58,860
His Majesty specifically ordered me

603
00:28:58,860 --> 00:29:00,260
to bring him to treat you.

604
00:29:01,730 --> 00:29:03,330
His Majesty also instructed

605
00:29:03,330 --> 00:29:05,460
that you should rest and recover well.

606
00:29:05,810 --> 00:29:06,750
Next year,

607
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:10,340
when the Yan millet ripens in the fields,

608
00:29:10,340 --> 00:29:11,740
we'll go see it together.

609
00:29:17,730 --> 00:29:18,140
Sure.

610
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:21,200
I will

611
00:29:23,490 --> 00:29:24,290
do my best.

612
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:44,700
This person suffers
from an incurable disease.

613
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:46,960
He was likely born with this affliction.

614
00:29:47,090 --> 00:29:48,490
Having not done anything until now,

615
00:29:48,490 --> 00:29:49,950
it's beyond medical help.

616
00:29:55,090 --> 00:29:55,900
The man inside

617
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:58,660
is a benefactor to everyone
in Great Xia.

618
00:29:58,850 --> 00:30:01,910
Please, Physician Xiao,
help him live a little longer—

619
00:30:02,710 --> 00:30:04,440
even if just to see one harvest.

620
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:05,620
I

621
00:30:06,550 --> 00:30:07,520
will do my best.

622
00:30:13,710 --> 00:30:16,460
[Agricultural Distribution Map]
[Yanwu Reserve Method]

623
00:30:23,450 --> 00:30:25,050
Don't worry, Your Highness.

624
00:30:26,300 --> 00:30:27,900
Since Physician Xiao is staying behind,

625
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:29,810
he must have a way to save Mr. Cen.

626
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:35,740
Let's hope so.

627
00:30:36,280 --> 00:30:42,870
[Agricultural Distribution Map 3]

628
00:30:48,490 --> 00:30:49,950
The men I promised to lend you

629
00:30:49,950 --> 00:30:51,610
will be waiting at the border.

630
00:30:52,100 --> 00:30:53,030
Though not many,

631
00:30:53,580 --> 00:30:55,180
they are all elite soldiers.

632
00:30:56,080 --> 00:30:57,280
After this succeeds,

633
00:30:58,040 --> 00:31:00,330
I hope our two nations
will remain allies forever

634
00:31:00,330 --> 00:31:01,730
and never wage war again.

635
00:31:05,570 --> 00:31:06,570
Are you so certain

636
00:31:07,180 --> 00:31:08,460
that I will be the victor?

637
00:31:08,460 --> 00:31:09,060
Of course.

638
00:31:10,180 --> 00:31:11,840
We are the same kind of person.

639
00:31:14,730 --> 00:31:17,420
You were forced
to become the prince of Yan State,

640
00:31:17,420 --> 00:31:17,980
while I

641
00:31:19,630 --> 00:31:21,960
reluctantly took the throne of Great Xia.

642
00:31:23,770 --> 00:31:26,100
Those around us commit all manner of evil,

643
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:28,580
yet we have become

644
00:31:28,610 --> 00:31:30,520
puppets despised by thousands.

645
00:31:31,470 --> 00:31:33,400
I once almost wanted to give up too.

646
00:31:33,900 --> 00:31:36,250
But then I met someone very important.

647
00:31:37,890 --> 00:31:39,150
She made me understand

648
00:31:39,980 --> 00:31:40,840
what an emperor

649
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:43,140
should truly do.

650
00:31:45,010 --> 00:31:47,530
As well as what
"heaven gave birth to the people"

651
00:31:47,530 --> 00:31:49,330
and ordained their fate" means.

652
00:31:50,770 --> 00:31:52,900
The way you Xia people speak in circles

653
00:31:53,140 --> 00:31:54,740
is beyond my understanding.

654
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:58,120
But you are a good emperor.

655
00:31:59,700 --> 00:32:00,900
That's why I must win.

656
00:32:05,320 --> 00:32:06,450
And you must win too.

657
00:32:08,250 --> 00:32:09,580
People in our positions

658
00:32:10,530 --> 00:32:13,040
bear too many responsibilities and hopes.

659
00:32:14,690 --> 00:32:16,210
We cannot be villains.

660
00:32:18,780 --> 00:32:20,370
We may not become friends,

661
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:23,430
but as long as I remain in Great Yan,

662
00:32:23,650 --> 00:32:24,910
Great Yan and Great Xia

663
00:32:26,390 --> 00:32:27,920
will never become enemies.

664
00:32:43,730 --> 00:32:45,990
Your Highness, someone's approaching.

665
00:32:46,770 --> 00:32:47,570
Hold on tight.

666
00:32:53,570 --> 00:32:54,310
Assassins!

667
00:32:54,330 --> 00:32:55,460
Protect our master!

668
00:33:17,370 --> 00:33:18,260
How insolent!

669
00:33:18,570 --> 00:33:20,670
How dare you defy the law
and attack people here?

670
00:33:20,670 --> 00:33:21,330
After them!

671
00:33:21,800 --> 00:33:22,580
Yes, Your Highness.

672
00:33:22,580 --> 00:33:23,310
My Lady.

673
00:33:24,530 --> 00:33:25,530
It's getting late

674
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:27,690
and your carriage is damaged.

675
00:33:27,690 --> 00:33:28,970
May I offer you a ride?

676
00:33:38,130 --> 00:33:39,330
May I ask where

677
00:33:40,780 --> 00:33:42,310
your residence is, My Lady?

678
00:33:44,980 --> 00:33:47,180
Your Highness surely knows how to jest.

679
00:33:47,420 --> 00:33:49,420
Please escort me back to the palace.

680
00:33:50,490 --> 00:33:52,690
I happened to be here on business today.

681
00:33:54,320 --> 00:33:56,780
If anything were to happen
to Your Highness,

682
00:33:57,120 --> 00:33:58,780
His Majesty would be furious,

683
00:33:59,840 --> 00:34:02,020
and we wouldn't be able
to bear the consequences.

684
00:34:02,020 --> 00:34:03,400
At this point,

685
00:34:04,570 --> 00:34:05,580
Prince Duan,

686
00:34:06,660 --> 00:34:08,670
just be straightforward

687
00:34:09,090 --> 00:34:10,150
with your mockery.

688
00:34:10,929 --> 00:34:13,130
You're quite favored in the palace now,

689
00:34:13,639 --> 00:34:15,100
unmatched in prominence.

690
00:34:16,659 --> 00:34:18,370
I'm simply happy for you.

691
00:34:18,820 --> 00:34:20,679
My relationship with His Majesty

692
00:34:21,130 --> 00:34:22,590
could hardly be something

693
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:24,980
you'd be happy about or anticipate.

694
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:25,840
Unless perhaps

695
00:34:26,219 --> 00:34:27,639
if I were to win his true affection,

696
00:34:27,639 --> 00:34:29,100
I would be of greater value

697
00:34:29,100 --> 00:34:30,270
to Your Highness?

698
00:34:31,850 --> 00:34:33,750
After all, controlling me

699
00:34:34,330 --> 00:34:37,060
would give you better leverage
over His Majesty.

700
00:34:39,449 --> 00:34:40,330
Yu Wanyin.

701
00:34:43,040 --> 00:34:45,219
Do you realize what you're saying?

702
00:34:57,980 --> 00:34:58,720
Xiahou Dan.

703
00:34:59,780 --> 00:35:00,840
The person you said

704
00:35:01,230 --> 00:35:02,560
is very important to you

705
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:05,220
is the Noble Consort, right?

706
00:35:08,010 --> 00:35:09,470
You must protect her well!

707
00:35:15,270 --> 00:35:16,620
Don't ever let her

708
00:35:18,260 --> 00:35:19,590
become another Shanyi.

709
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:20,720
Your Majesty!

710
00:35:22,610 --> 00:35:23,410
Your Majesty.

711
00:35:27,610 --> 00:35:28,340
Your Majesty.

712
00:35:28,340 --> 00:35:28,870
Bad news.

713
00:35:29,710 --> 00:35:31,870
The officials who haven't taken sides
have fallen ill

714
00:35:31,870 --> 00:35:32,670
or died.

715
00:35:34,040 --> 00:35:35,570
He fears your spies

716
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:38,130
and dares not leave the palace.

717
00:35:39,630 --> 00:35:41,720
He knows you intend to kill us,

718
00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:44,860
yet still sends me, a mere woman, to go

719
00:35:45,690 --> 00:35:46,950
just to demonstrate

720
00:35:47,770 --> 00:35:49,210
that he is a wise ruler.

721
00:35:50,110 --> 00:35:51,350
So you mean

722
00:35:52,550 --> 00:35:54,150
your trip outside the palace

723
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:57,640
was His Majesty
sending you to win people over for him?

724
00:35:58,300 --> 00:35:59,900
And that his favor toward you

725
00:36:00,420 --> 00:36:01,680
isn't genuine either?

726
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:06,740
That's quite a statement.

727
00:36:07,730 --> 00:36:09,440
Are you any different?

728
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,810
Since I entered the palace,

729
00:36:14,350 --> 00:36:16,750
everyone claims their heart belongs to me,

730
00:36:17,460 --> 00:36:18,770
but deep down,

731
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:22,860
isn't it all just manipulation

732
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:24,960
and exploitation?

733
00:36:28,050 --> 00:36:28,980
You have a point.

734
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:33,360
But for someone as clever as Wanyin,

735
00:36:34,610 --> 00:36:36,700
couldn't you find a way to refuse him?

736
00:36:38,090 --> 00:36:39,220
Why should I refuse?

737
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,980
This is my best opportunity

738
00:36:41,980 --> 00:36:44,240
to scout an escape route from the palace.

739
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:46,410
You want to

740
00:36:48,270 --> 00:36:48,900
escape?

741
00:36:49,620 --> 00:36:50,340
Your Majesty!

742
00:36:50,340 --> 00:36:51,010
Your Majesty!

743
00:36:51,010 --> 00:36:52,490
I've already sent the Imperial Guards
to rescue Her Highness.

744
00:36:52,490 --> 00:36:55,010
-Your Majesty, you can't go!
-She's in danger. I need to save her.

745
00:36:55,010 --> 00:36:55,300
Dan!

746
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:56,010
-Let go!
-Your Majesty.

747
00:36:56,010 --> 00:36:56,380
Dan!

748
00:36:57,130 --> 00:36:57,980
You don't know martial arts.

749
00:36:57,980 --> 00:36:58,990
If you leave the palace,

750
00:36:58,990 --> 00:37:00,300
I fear I cannot protect you.

751
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:01,840
What if something happens to her?

752
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:02,350
Let go!

753
00:37:02,610 --> 00:37:03,170
-Your Majesty.
-Dan!

754
00:37:03,170 --> 00:37:03,680
Dan!

755
00:37:09,610 --> 00:37:10,290
Mr. Bei.

756
00:37:11,750 --> 00:37:12,390
You go.

757
00:37:14,210 --> 00:37:15,410
Only you can save her.

758
00:37:16,260 --> 00:37:16,860
Please, will you go?

759
00:37:16,860 --> 00:37:17,660
If I go,

760
00:37:17,740 --> 00:37:18,940
who will protect you?

761
00:37:19,110 --> 00:37:19,650
But Mr. Bei...

762
00:37:19,650 --> 00:37:20,300
You cannot go!
